---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure | Tall Chair Advisor"
  description="Tall Chair Advisor affiliate disclosure — how our links work, what commissions we receive, and why they never influence our chair evaluations."
  noindex={true}
>
  <main class="container-wide py-16">
    <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold text-heading mb-8">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>

      <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6">
        <strong>Last Updated:</strong> December 2025
      </p>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-heading mb-4">Our Commitment to Transparency</h2>
        <p class="text-body mb-4">
          Tall Chair Advisor is committed to transparency with our readers. This disclosure
          explains how we may earn revenue through affiliate relationships while maintaining
          our editorial independence.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-heading mb-4">How We Earn Revenue</h2>
        <p class="text-body mb-4">
          Some links on our website are affiliate links. This means that if you click on a
          link and make a purchase, we may receive a small commission at no additional cost
          to you. These commissions help support our work and allow us to continue providing
          free content.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-heading mb-4">Editorial Independence</h2>
        <p class="text-body mb-4">
          Our reviews and recommendations are based on our independent research, testing,
          and analysis. Affiliate relationships do not influence our editorial content,
          product ratings, or recommendations. We recommend products we believe offer
          genuine value to our readers, regardless of affiliate status.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-heading mb-4">Affiliate Partners</h2>
        <p class="text-body mb-4">
          We may participate in affiliate programs with various retailers and manufacturers
          of office furniture and ergonomic products. The specific affiliate programs we
          participate in may change over time.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-heading mb-4">Your Trust Matters</h2>
        <p class="text-body mb-4">
          We understand that trust is earned. Our goal is to provide honest, helpful
          information that assists tall and large individuals in finding comfortable,
          supportive seating. We will never recommend a product solely because of an
          affiliate relationship.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-heading mb-4">Questions</h2>
        <p class="text-body">
          If you have questions about our affiliate relationships or this disclosure,
          please contact us through our <a href="/contact/" class="link-internal">Contact page</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>
